So in other words, it's like you can't compute them,

00:19:30.219 --> 00:19:31.939
they're just not especially great.

00:19:31.939 --> 00:19:33.439
And just in case you were wondering,

00:19:33.439 --> 00:19:36.000
you would probably use the conformal inference there

00:19:36.000 --> 00:19:37.439
and they sort of align pretty well.

00:19:37.439 --> 00:19:40.520
